profile:
D&S renovations offers residential renovations services in Nova Scotia.  Full scope renovations, basements developments, kitchens, bathrooms renovations, exteriors and home additions are just some of the services offered by D&S.  With over 50 years of experience in the residential construction industry D&S Renovations has developed our services to meet the needs of all clients and their budgets. 

Please give us a call today to inquire about an estimate with one of our project developers.

profile:
I love renovations was born early in 2013. The name says it all, Chris and Mike have a passion for creating and building renovations. Both love working after hours on their own projects and never tire of the constant problem solving opportunities and amazing people they meet day to day. Focusing on customer service comes naturally for this team, having both spent years working in the food and beverage industry including some of the highest ranking properties in Canada.

We don’t merely renovate homes, because it’s what we sell. We create renovations, because of our fundamental values. When we renovate homes, it’s about more than the finished product. It’s about the families we work with, the spaces we transform and the relationships that we build.
